abstract.text: A key-value map of context-specific query string parameters specifying the behavior of different API importing operations. The following shows operation-specific parameters and their supported values. To exclude DocumentationParts from the import, set parameters as ignore=documentation. To configure the endpoint type, set parameters as endpointConfigurationTypes=EDGE, endpointConfigurationTypes=REGIONAL, or endpointConfigurationTypes=PRIVATE. The default endpoint type is EDGE. To handle imported basepath, set parameters as basepath=ignore, basepath=prepend or basepath=split.
